            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#医师劝阻100斤要做减重手术的人#】据不完全统计，去年我国实施减重代谢手术超3.5万例。医师介绍，#不是每个人都适合做减重手术#，只有在运动、饮食和药...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%8C%BB%E5%B8%88%E5%8A%9D%E9%98%BB100%E6%96%A4%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E5%87%8F%E9%87%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%8C%BB%E5%B8%88%E5%8A%9D%E9%98%BB100%E6%96%A4%E8%A6%81%E5%81%9A%E5%87%8F%E9%87%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF%E7%9A%84%E4%BA%BA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#医师劝阻100斤要做减重手术的人#</span></a>】据不完全统计，去年我国实施减重代谢手术超3.5万例。医师介绍，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E5%81%9A%E5%87%8F%E9%87%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF%23&amp;extparam=%23%E4%B8%8D%E6%98%AF%E6%AF%8F%E4%B8%AA%E4%BA%BA%E9%83%BD%E9%80%82%E5%90%88%E5%81%9A%E5%87%8F%E9%87%8D%E6%89%8B%E6%9C%AF%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#不是每个人都适合做减重手术#</span></a>，只有在运动、饮食和药物干预效果都不理想的前提下才考虑手术。此外，减重手术只是解决由肥胖带来的健康威胁，后续还得靠良好的饮食、运动习惯来保持👇🏻（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5011379044941833" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hnp22kx0nwj61ur11khdt02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/T90Z00Jjlx08dfg1daJG010412019n2x0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710464526&amp;ssig=shG8ModYlX&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/q6MEocnNlx08dffZOtSE01041200CXqC0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1G