        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【[吃惊]严重会致命！#广东人注意这种甘蔗千万不要吃#】近日，广东发布提示，当心霉变甘蔗，吃了会引起食物中毒！初春季节，甘蔗在运输及储存的过程中，很容易发...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[吃惊]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/default/d_chijing-59b444adb6.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span>严重会致命！<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E7%94%98%E8%94%97%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%90%83%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E8%BF%99%E7%A7%8D%E7%94%98%E8%94%97%E5%8D%83%E4%B8%87%E4%B8%8D%E8%A6%81%E5%90%83%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#广东人注意这种甘蔗千万不要吃#</span></a>】近日，广东发布提示，当心霉变甘蔗，吃了会引起食物中毒！初春季节，甘蔗在运输及储存的过程中，很容易发生霉变产生毒素，引起的食物中毒。甘蔗霉变后会产生一种神经毒素，短时间内引起中枢神经系统损伤，严重可致缺血、呼吸衰竭死亡。质软、变色、酒味、长毛、红心的甘蔗都不建议吃。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%B8%85%E6%98%8E%E7%94%98%E8%94%97%E6%AF%92%E8%BF%87%E8%9B%87%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B9%BF%E4%B8%9C%E4%BA%BA%E6%B3%A8%E6%84%8F%E6%B8%85%E6%98%8E%E7%94%98%E8%94%97%E6%AF%92%E8%BF%87%E8%9B%87%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#广东人注意清明甘蔗毒过蛇#</span></a><a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5011117018120215" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">第一现场的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax1.sinaimg.cn/orj480/6aac5feagy1hno7yfyulrj20u01hc0vk.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/LTMlkkF3gx08de89TAeY010412008khw0E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=720x1280.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710464526&amp;ssig=IFbYBoJ1C4&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/LDetnlndgx08de8b6kWs0104120059GK0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=540x960.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710464526&amp;ssig=oYAdQEUb%2BA&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/u0/pHFJnjcagx08de89nwco010412002SJs0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=360x640.24.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710464526&amp;ssig=BKjbiwnJEg&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5011117018120215" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
